2026-06-30T20:59:10 | INFO | INTERACTION {"session_id": "979747e8991f44289a60ade132846257", "question": "how do i register for course", "answer": "To register for a course at the University of Dar es Salaam (UDSM), please follow these steps:\n\n1. Check your email for course registration notifications from the UDSM portal.\n2. Log in to the UDSM portal using your credentials (username and password).\n3. Navigate to the Course Registration section.\n4. Select the courses you wish to register for, considering any prerequisites or restrictions.\n5. Confirm your selections and proceed with registration.\n\nPlease note that course registration timelines may vary depending on the semester or academic year. Be sure to check the UDSM portal and your email regularly for updates.\n\nIf you encounter any issues during registration, please contact the relevant faculty office or the IT department at UDSM for assistance.", "source": "LLM", "response_time": 26.31, "retrieved_context": []}
