2026-06-30T21:00:40 | INFO | INTERACTION {"session_id": "979747e8991f44289a60ade132846257", "question": "when is semester 2 ending", "answer": "According to the provided context, the END OF 2025/2026 ACADEMIC YEAR for all students EXCEPT MCHAS (Master of Chas?) is on July 31, 2026.\n\nFor MCHAS students, the exact date is not specified in the given context.", "source": "LLM", "response_time": 8.3, "retrieved_context": [{"text": "nday 24 November 2025 Ends: - Friday 05 December 2025 B. TEACHING AND EXAMINATION 1ST SEMESTER-EXCEPT FOR MCHAS Begins: - Monday 24 November 2025 Lecture Sessions End: - Thursday 05 March 2026 Ends: - Friday 20 March 2026 MID-SEMESTER BREATHER Begins: - Saturday 20 December 2025 Ends: - Saturday 27 December 2025 1ST SEMESTER UNIVERSITY COURSEWORK ASSESSMENT WEEK Begins: - Tuesday 13 January 2026 Ends: - Thursday 15 January 2026 1ST SEMESTER EXAMINATIONS - EXCEPT FOR MCHAS Begins: - Friday 06 Mar", "source": "ALMANAC_2025-2026.pdf", "doc_id": "3a9f2fc5a0fb4a658cfd7c6c2a3d802c", "start": 3600, "end": 4100, "score": 0.6538}, {"text": "RIENTATION WEEK Begins: - Monday 17 November 2025 Ends: - Saturday 22 November 2025 REGISTRATION OF NEW UNDERGRADUATE AND POSTGRADUATE STUDENTS Begins: - Monday 17 November 2025 Ends: - Friday 28 November 2025 Postgraduate Students Orientation Day - Friday 28 November 2025 Continuing Students Report - Saturday 22 November 2025 REGISTRATION OF CONTINUING STUDENTS FOR THE FIRST SEMESTER Begins: - Monday 24 November 2025 Ends: - Friday 05 December 2025 B. TEACHING AND EXAMINATION 1ST SEMESTER-EXCEP", "source": "ALMANAC_2025-2026.pdf", "doc_id": "3a9f2fc5a0fb4a658cfd7c6c2a3d802c", "start": 3200, "end": 3700, "score": 0.6377}, {"text": "- Friday 17 April 2026 2ND SEMESTER UNIVERSITY COURSEWORK ASSESSMENT WEEK Begins: - Tuesday 26 May 2026 Ends: - Thursday 28 May 2026 2ND SEMESTER EXAMINATIONS - EXCEPT FOR MCHAS Begins: - Friday 17 July 2026 Ends: - Friday 31 July 2026 END OF 2025/2026 ACADEMIC YEAR: 31 JULY 2026 - EXCEPT FOR MCHAS MARKING - EXCEPT FOR MCHAS Begins: - Monday 03 August 2026 Ends: - Friday 21 August 2026 COMPILATION - EXCEPT FOR MCHAS Begins: - Monday 24 August 2026 Ends: - Friday 28 August 2026\n5\nRELEASE OF PROVI", "source": "ALMANAC_2025-2026.pdf", "doc_id": "3a9f2fc5a0fb4a658cfd7c6c2a3d802c", "start": 4800, "end": 5300, "score": 0.5964}]}
